			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="medium-6 columns">
			<a href="https://instagram.com/absoluttweb/" target="_blank" class="btn-instagram">
				<h5><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i> Instagram</h5>
				<p>Design og Mockups</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
